{"content": "I need to multiply 640 \u00d7 837 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 640\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 0 = 486 + 36 + 0 = 522\u2081\u2080\n- 837\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 7\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 7 = 648 + 27 + 7 = 682\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 522 \u00d7 682 = 356,004\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 356004 \u00f7 9 = 39556 r 0\n- 39556 \u00f7 9 = 4395 r 1\n- 4395 \u00f7 9 = 488 r 3\n- 488 \u00f7 9 = 54 r 2\n- 54 \u00f7 9 = 6 r 0\n- 6 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 6\n\nReading from bottom to top: **602310\u2089**\n\n602310", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 340}